{"tid":379056,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"精神科醫生建議家長多留意子女情緒避免他們患上抑鬱症","createTime":"2017-08-29T03:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T03:30:56.000Z","uid":13468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1fdf41701247a8a4721f9306f528572da486043d","tid":379056,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:19:32.000Z","msg":"精神科醫生建議家長多留意子女情緒避免他們患上抑鬱症<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開學在即，學童面對各種壓力，可能會有焦慮。青山醫院兒童及青少年精神科副顧問醫生陳君訥表示，現時每一百個兒童，就有兩個患上抑鬱症或焦慮症，而每一百名青少年，則有三至八個有這些症狀，幸而未有上升趨勢。她指，兒童壓力主要來自學業、朋輩及家庭等，並非單一原因導致，而學生在考試前是面對壓力的高峰期。<br />\n<br />\n陳君訥建議家長多留意子女是否有抑鬱症的徵狀，如果經常不開心，對任何事物失去興趣等，就要及早求醫。她又指，家長應支持子女一起面對焦慮，嘗試將問題分拆，逐一解決，以消除子女面對的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=961021&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D961021%26csid%3D261_341&d=CBxb65HEqgX8oStXjL8iVGxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=c205a96a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=961021&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"7f6d7de488b69ff0030e273adbb21f8f14b70c76","tid":379056,"uid":7903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192356042a20a0d059a2b5db195c8f5df4b1081b","tid":379056,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"對任何事物沒有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f09a0d561f3ce1c6f6cded487ac9c6e06fa775","tid":379056,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T03:25:32.000Z","msg":"留意完有咩用？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a756fa263fa161eee569ef7d0e0af8a1db68d21","tid":379056,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-2